<br>
Those who want spoilers can find them easily, those who don't want them don't try. I suggest having the word &quot;SPOILER&quot; in all caps in the subject of the message, so those who want to find out for themselves don't accidentally read the message. I also think they should be kept in the general section, and not the flame boards. This is a place for half-truths and misinformation, not legitimate knowledge.<br>
<br>
As has been said, I feel that removing posts is unnecessary and is censorship. We established that some censorship is necessary and good... but I disagree most strongly with removing something that is inoffensive and for the most part harmless. And I question why it was done in the first place. <p>Lauriston Pianoforte<!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->That Guy<!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->Bard of Quellious</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub54.ezboard.com/bquelliousquaterstherebirth.showUserPublicProfile?gid=esmalyn>Esmalyn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>The Bitch Queen</span><br>  Posts: 562<br> <font color=#00CCFF>(10/28/02 6:49:17 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub54.ezboard.com/fquelliousquaterstherebirthfrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=617.topic&index=33>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Says I am banned but</span><hr size=1> /em points at Lauriston<br>
